<td><img class="tex" alt="\underbrace{s_P(t) = \sum_{k=-\infty}^{\infty} S[k] \cdot e^{i 2\pi \frac{k}{P} t}}_{\text{Poisson summation formula (Fourier series)}}" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/3/9/e/39e026ff285c6513d464e71192f144d9.png" /></td>
