<p><img class="tex" alt="\sum_{n=-\infty}^{\infty} s[n]\cdot \delta(t-nT) = \underbrace{\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} S_{1/T}(f)\cdot e^{i 2\pi f t}\,df}_{\text{inverse Fourier transform}} " src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/a/a/5/aa5dace7130b217e38bcb779d94d589d.png" /></p>
